Package com.risk.maputils

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EditMap
    This class loads a map from an existing domination map file, or if file doesn't exits creates a new map from scratch.
    EditMapTest
    This is test class for EditMap
    MapOperations
    This class defined different operation on class such as continent add and remove for adding and remove continent from continent list country add and remove for adding and remove country from country list neighbor add and remove for adding and remove adjacent countries from list
    MapOperationsTest
    This test class is for map operations.
    MapUtilsTestSuite
    Test Suite for Map Utils
    MapValidator
    This class performs validation of map correctness, also after loading and saving any new map the map should be validated automatically.
    MapValidatorTest
    This is the test class for the MapValidator.
    MapWriter
    The class MapWriter will write the data in map file when the user creates a map
    ShowMap
    This Class is used for displaying the loaded map as well as displaying the game map.
